rs of up to $3.0 billion to acquire additional equity interests in these VIEs.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style="margin-bottom:9pt;text-align:justify;text-indent:27pt"&gt;&lt;span style="color:#000000;font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;font-size:10pt;font-weight:400;line-height:120%"&gt;Investments held in our non-marketable equity investment portfolios are subject to equity price risk.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</meta:NonMarketableEquityInvestmentsTextBlock>
